originalText.text:
FRANK SIMMONS BAND WILL MAKE YOUR NIGHT UNFORGETTABLE! Wow, it has been a few weeks since our wedding and we cannot stop talking about The Frank Simmons Band. Our venue, Crystal Plaza, highly recommended this band and we are SO happy we booked them.

Everyone we worked with at Hank Lane from Ian in Sales, to Russ to help walk through our music tastes, to Frank and the band- everyone is amazing. Their #1 goal is to make sure you have an incredible night and a FUN time!

Our dance floor was packed the entire night, so much so that guests refused to leave! Our friends and family cannot get over how great the band was- they felt like they were at a concert. Frank Simmons Band is THE best to book for the best wedding ever!!!

originalText.text: BROOKLYN SOUND was amazing. They are true professionals and it shows. I'm a musician myself and noticed more details than the average person. Fantastic energy. Super talented musicians and singers. Choreographed dance moves, singers are always moving and shaking. Switching seamlessly from one song to the next with no stops - this takes a lot of preparation and coordination. Great job guiding the reception through its various elements (individual dances, speeches, eating, dance party) without missing a beat and keeping some mellow music going even during the meals to maintain the vibe. Great MC tone (no cheesy "ready to rumble" vibe). They suggested starting off with a 15 - 20 minute dance party setting, with some other dance party sets between salad and main course. We were skeptical (it might feel too chopped up, hadn't seen this done before), but it was SO GOOD. Definitely recommend that. Made it feel like the whole event was a party with a couple breaks, not a dinner lowering the energy followed by attempts to re-energize the crowd with the party. And they let some of the family jump up and play some songs with them (on our own instruments).

originalText.text: My husband and I couldn't be happier that we went with Hank Lane's Dane Wright Band for our wedding! They are so talented and brought the best energy to our big day. The dance floor was packed all night, and we received tons of compliments from our guests. The band leader (Dane) also met with us personally before the wedding to discuss musical preferences and event flow. You will not regret booking them!!!

originalText.text:
Our wedding day was made truly unforgettable, and we owe a massive part of that to the phenomenal Russ Bennett Band at Hank Lane. If you're searching for a band that can flawlessly pull together an eclectic mix of songs and elevate the energy of your event to new heights, look no further!

From the very beginning, Russ Bennett showcased his exceptional talent as a band leader. His ability to read the room and adapt the music to suit the mood and preferences of our guests was nothing short of impressive. Russ and his band's versatility allowed them to perform a wide range of songs, literally making any musical request possible. Whether it was a romantic ballad or a high-energy dance track, they nailed it every time.

What stood out the most was the sheer enthusiasm and infectious energy that radiated from the stage. Russ Bennett had an uncanny ability to connect with our guests, drawing them onto the dance floor and keeping them there all night long. Even the band's singers couldn't resist the temptation to join in the festivities. Seeing them dance and jump into the photo booth was a delightful surprise and added an extra layer of fun to the evening.

The Russ Bennett Band not only delivered on musical excellence but also on the overall experience they provided. They were professional, accommodating, and genuinely passionate about making our wedding day extraordinary. Their attention to detail and commitment to our vision left us feeling incredibly grateful.

If we could, we would hire the Russ Bennett Band again and again for any future function. They transformed our wedding celebration into a musical journey that we and our guests will cherish forever. If you want a wedding band that can truly do it all and create unforgettable memories, don't hesitate to book the Russ Bennett Band. We can't recommend them enough!

Book them, it will ABSOLUTELY be worth it!
